description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1:

C&B expose today's Fauciite covid lie. They joke: Did DeSantis do it? Blue states have highest covid rates. Liz Cheney (who "first of all, is a fraud," says Clay) reads Mark Meadows text messages at January 6th hearing. C&B question if such message reading is even allowed. Caller on Colorado's governor.
